data.title: The War Diary 1939-1945
data.meta_description: Schiffer Military History, 1996. First edition. Hardcover. First American printing, near fine cloth hardcover shows just a touch of shelf wear including light bumping to couple of corners, in near fine dust jacket price at flap that shows just a hint of wear as well. 608 pages with index and a couple sets of black & whites. Nice copy of this war diary from the noted German general. Near Fine in Near Fine Dust Jacket.
